msgstr "请在 link:https://www.youtube.com/quarkusio[Quarkus YouTube 频道] 观看完整视频。该基准测试代码可在 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison[github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison] 上获取。"
